WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
How to adjust?

00:00:03.523 --> 00:00:10.000
"Amblyopia is decreased vision of one of the two eyes, the brain ignores full or partial contribution of one of them"

00:00:11.861 --> 00:00:16.000
You need: 
-smartphone 
 -3d glasses 

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:23.000
You can create your own glasses with cardboard, cellophane or acetate paper

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:24.300
not use pale-colored

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.000
Start the app in your smartphone 

00:00:26.514 --> 00:00:32.174
You will see something like this ... two main colors in the game

00:00:32.174 --> 00:00:36.394
The idea is that the two eyes will work together

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:42.420
with the eyeglasses help, one eye will see the falling blocks and  the other eye will see the blocks that build.

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:46.380
How to adjust?

00:00:46.380 --> 00:00:49.400
In the option "Adjust color" or "Change color"

00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:54.960
put up your glass
( In this case Red= left, blue= right)

00:00:54.960 --> 00:01:02.240
Close the right eye to adjust the left color eye through the "LEFT" text

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:04.240

00:01:10.220 --> 00:01:16.900
Choose MAGENTA color ( with red glass turns white)

00:01:17.703 --> 00:01:21.583
Now we adjust the right eye

00:01:21.583 --> 00:01:26.803
Close the left eye to adjust the rigth color eye through the "RIGHT" text

00:01:35.614 --> 00:01:43.754
Choose Cian color ( with blue glass turns white)

00:01:44.178 --> 00:01:49.638
you will see the game as well

00:01:52.007 --> 00:01:56.367
With both eyes you will form a complete set
.....

00:01:57.987 --> 00:02:01.427
If you play 1 Hour a day you will see significant improvements in 6 weeks of use

00:02:01.427 --> 00:02:05.927
need internet connection to play

00:02:05.927 --> 00:02:09.487
Get well soon!

